data.description: Check out this adorable stone home that is sitting on over four flat acres in Mount Pleasant Twp. Upon walking in you'll be greeted by the family room that offers tons of natural light and is kept cozy with a pellet stove. The family room flows into the kitchen that is completely updated with solid hickory cabinets, granite counters and stainless appliances. Conveniently located off of the kitchen is first floor laundry as well as a mud room. There are three bedrooms and one full bath on the main level. The basement is unfinished with high ceilings and leaves tons of possibilities. Off of the basement is an internal one car garage. Enjoy your coffee on the new trex deck that overlooks the amazing backyard space. In addition, there is an outbuilding to hold all of your toys and tractor. Make this home yours just in time to enjoy the new inground pool this summer!
